      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Hild runs the only inn in Stairwatch. She sees everyone who passes through and hears everything worth hearing. She asks no questions â€” but she notices everything. If something unusual happens in Stairwatch, Hild knows about it.</p>",
          "director": "<p>Use Hild as an information funnel. She won't volunteer gossip, but if the PCs ask the right questions or earn her trust, she provides better intel than any Chainwarden.</p>"
