        "description": {
          "value": "<p>If the PCs earn Hild's respect â€” by helping with the mine task or treating Lew well â€” she packs extra rations for their departure, on the house. She represents the stubborn, practical generosity that Fimbulwinter hasn't been able to kill.</p>",
          "director": "<p>Hild packs rations quietly, without ceremony. She doesn't call it a gift. \"He owes me. Don't let him forget.\"</p>"
