        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A stranger asks Hild about the PCs' destination. She says nothing to the stranger. But she finds the PCs afterward and tells them quietly: \"Someone was asking about you. I said I hadn't seen you. They didn't believe me.\"</p>",
          "director": "<p>This is a Grafvitnir Pressure Check. A network contact (not Dreyfus) was asking about the PCs' destination. Hild's warning gives the party advance notice they've been tracked.</p>"
